    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "爱国者M4——当你在塔科夫需要捍卫生命、自由和追求战利品的权利时，它便是完美之选。没有什么比带着星条旗的烈焰杀出一条胜利之路更能诠释“自由”真谛。乔治·华盛顿也会为之自豪。",
      "en": "The Patriot M4 - perfect for when you need to defend your right to life, liberty, and the pursuit of loot in Tarkov. Because nothing says 'freedom' quite like shooting your way to victory with stars and stripes blazing. George Washington would be proud."
    },
